snippet.title: Mythic Ocean - NS/XB1/PS4 (Demo available)
snippet.description:
Teach the gods to create a better world - or mess it all up in Mythic Ocean!

Play the Demo now on your Nintendo Switch™ and Xbox One or Xbox Series X|S!

We will also publish Mythic Ocean to PS4™ - Stay tuned for this announcement.

Mythic Ocean is made by the lovely, passionate and talented Paralune team.
http://mythicoceangame.com
